<template>
    <v-container
        fluid
    >
        <v-data-table
                :headers="headers"
                :items="requests"
                sort-by="email"
        >
            <template v-slot:item.actions="{ item }">
                <v-btn
                        @click="requestHandled(item)"
                        x-small
                        color="success"
                >
                  Contacted
                </v-btn>
            </template>

        </v-data-table>
    </v-container>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        name: "InfoRequests",
        data: () => ({
            headers: [
                {
                    text: "Email",
                    align: "start",
                    value: "email"
                },
                {
                    text: "First Name",
                    align: "start",
                    value: "firstName"
                },
                {
                    text: "Last Name",
                    align: "start",
                    value: "lastName",
                },
                {
                    text: "Opportunity",
                    align: "start",
                    value: "opportunity"
                },
                {
                    text: "Actions",
                    value: "actions",
                    sortable: false
                }
            ],
            requests: [
                {
                    id: 0,
                    firstName: "John",
                    lastName: "Does",
                    email: "johndoe@example.com",
                    opportunity: "Example Job"
                },
                {
                    id: 1,
                    firstName: "John",
                    lastName: "Does",
                    email: "johndoe@example.com",
                    opportunity: "Example Job"
                },
                {
                    id: 2,
                    firstName: "John",
                    lastName: "Does",
                    email: "johndoe@example.com",
                    opportunity: "Example Job"
                },
                {
                    id: 3,
                    firstName: "John",
                    lastName: "Does",
                    email: "johndoe@example.com",
                    opportunity: "Example Job"
                },
            ]
        }),
        methods: {
            requestHandled: function (request) {
                this.deleteItem(request)
            },
            deleteItem: function(req) {
                this.requests = this.requests.filter(function(request){
                    return req.id !== request.id
                })
            }
        }
    }
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
